This paper is primarily focused on regularization techniques for deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper specifically applies these techniques to image segmentation tasks (cs.CV) and classification tasks (cs.AI), indicating a focus on computer vision applications. The paper also discusses the complexity of computing function norms in DNNs, which is a topic related to computational complexity (cs.DS) and neural networks (cs.NE).
